### File Structure
- **App Routing (Next.js App Router):**
  - `app/` - Main application pages using Next.js App Router with server components
    - `page.tsx` - Landing page
    - `layout.tsx` - Root layout with providers
    - `dashboard/` - Dashboard pages (Overview, Performance, Portfolio, Transactions, etc.)
    - `auth/` - Authentication pages (Login, Register, Reset Password)
    - `api/` - API routes for backend functionality

- **Components:**
  - `components/ui/` - Reusable UI components (shadcn/ui)
  - `components/dashboard/` - Dashboard-specific components
  - `components/overview/` - Overview page components
  - `components/performance/` - Performance page components
  - `components/portfolio/` - Portfolio page components
  - `components/transactions/` - Transaction page components
  - `components/import/` - CSV import components
  - `components/calculator/` - Calculator components
  - `components/shared/` - Shared components used across multiple features
  - `components/landing/` - Landing page components
  - `components/auth/` - Authentication components

- **Utilities and Services:**
  - `lib/` - Utility functions and service classes
    - `lib/supabase.ts` - Supabase client setup
    - `lib/utils.ts` - General utility functions
    - `lib/api.ts` - API utility functions
  
- **State Management:**
  - `providers/` - React Context providers
  - `hooks/` - Custom React hooks

- **Types:**
  - `types/` - TypeScript type definitions

- **Database:**
  - `supabase/migrations/` - SQL migrations for Supabase
  - `supabase/functions/` - Supabase Edge Functions

### Code Style
- **TypeScript:** Strict typing with interfaces for all data structures
- **Tailwind CSS:** Utility-first CSS for styling with custom theme
- **Component Organization:** Modular components with clear separation of concerns
- **Naming Conventions:** PascalCase for components, camelCase for functions/variables
- **API Handling:** Centralized API functions with error handling 